## Game Summary

- A chaotic, cooperative potion-shop simulator set inside a living, trap-filled dungeon.
- The target audience is casual players. Prioritize fun and chaos over complex mechanics. All generated mechanics must be simple to learn but allow for emergent, funny failures.

## Core Mechanics

- Throwable potions that causes some effects to the players or the environment. The players can use them to their advantage.
- The dungeon map are shifting after each day, becoming deadlier and more difficult over time.